description:
In the past years there have appeared a lot of new frameworks and
libraries in the modern web world, but behind the scenes there are a
lot of similarities and standards in any language and I will talk
about these standards.

I also have a post about it:
https://medium.com/@ent1c3d/similarities-between-django-and-laravel-eb5e2b344ecb
title: Similarities and standards between modern web frameworks
